		<pb n="2"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; <date>April 4&#44; 1854</date>.</p>
			<p rend="align(right)"><date>6<hi rend="sup">th</hi> of Nissan</date></p>
			<p>Peace and all good forever&#44; very honored sir&#58;</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">I have received your honored letter of yesterday&#39;s date&#44;<lb/> and I must reply to you that your conclusion was quite correct. I have&#44;<lb/> in fact&#44; forgotten to enclose the money&#44; and when I returned from the<lb/> <sic>postoffice</sic>&#44; I noticed it. I have sent four Haggadoth with English<lb/> translation to <placeName>St. Louis</placeName>.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">With wishes for a happy holiday&#44; I sign</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">Respectfully&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(4)">Your most devoted&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">Michael</persName>&#44; son of <persName>Rabbi Abraham</persName></p> 
          <p rend="indent(8)"><persName>Uri</persName></p>
          <p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">Michael Light</persName></p>
